{
  "chapter": 76,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十六回《生死一线间》围绕三条线索展开。荆无命突然出现，向松因右手已废的荆无命而轻敌挑衅，却被荆无命右手一剑封喉，揭示其右手比左手更快的秘密。荆无命随后救走林仙儿，林仙儿以机敏的分析洞悉荆无命反叛上官金虹的动机，主动跟随。阿飞在林仙儿离去后陷入绝望，躺在血泊中几近死亡。与此同时，上官金虹送来决斗战书，约李寻欢后天在城外长亭决斗。孙小红为李寻欢准备纸笔记录遗言，表白愿与他生死相随的决心。孙老先生理解李寻欢不会逃避的性格，点明他必须赴约。李寻欢先行勘察决斗场地，孙老先生向孙小红解说高手决斗中天时地利的重要性。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "在下虽不懂杀人，却还能杀，荆先生虽懂得杀人，只可惜杀人并不是用嘴的，是要用手！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "你看不到我的手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "手也有很多种，我看到的并不是杀人的手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "你认为我右手不能杀人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "人也有很多种，有些人容易杀，有些人不容易。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "你是哪一种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你杀不死的那一种。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "原来你恨我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "不恨你的人只怕还很少。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "你想杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "想杀你的人也不止我一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "但你为什么要等到现在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "要杀人就得等机会，这道理你本该比谁都明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "你认为现在机会已来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "只可惜我有个秘密你还不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_song",
      "speaker_name": "向松",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "什么秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_xiang_song",
      "text": "我右手也能杀人的，而且比左手更快！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们既已听到了我的秘密，还想走？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "想不到你会来救我。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你以为我是来救你的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "也许我知道你的意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你来救我，只因为上官金虹要杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你恨他，所以只要是他想做的事，你就要破坏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "直到现在，我才总算知道了你这个人，才知道上官飞也是你杀的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你知道得太多了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我也知道你绝不会杀我，因为你若杀了我，岂非正如了上官金虹的心愿？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你非但不会杀我，而且还会带我走的，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "带你走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "因为你既不能让我死在上官金虹手上，又不愿让我泄露你的秘密，所以你只有带我走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我也心甘情愿跟着你去，无论你要到哪里，我都跟着。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看过皇历，后天不是好日子，诸事不宜。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "杀人又何必选好日子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你能不能杀他？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说，我写。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你还有什么未了的心愿？还有什么未做完的事？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你现在就要我说？我还没有死呀。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "等你死了，就说不出了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "无论什么事你都可以说出来，譬如说——阿飞，你还有什么话要对他说的？还有什么事要为他做的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "没有？什么都没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我可以要他不去杀别人，却无法要他不去爱别人！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "别人若要杀他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "现在还有谁要杀他？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上官金虹……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "上官金虹既然肯放他走，就绝不会再杀他，否则他现在早就死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可是，以后呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "无论多长的梦，都总有醒的时候，等到他清醒的那天，什么事他自己都会明白的，现在我说了也没有用。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么，她呢？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你……你若有什么话，有什么事……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "没有，什么都没有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "她活着，自然会有人照顾她；她死了，也有人埋葬。什么事都用不着我来关心，我死了对她只有好处。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你为什么不肯对我说？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你为什么一定要我说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说了，我就记下来；你若死了，我就一件件替你去做，然后……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "然后怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "然后我就死！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你……你为什么要死？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不能不死，因为你若死了，我活着一定比死更难受。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你若要我活着，你自己就不能死……上官金虹也并不是一定要找你决斗，他对你始终有几分畏惧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我们可以走，走得远远的，什么事都不管，我……我可以带你回家，那地方从没有人知道，上官金虹就算还是想来找你，也休想找得到。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "无论你怎么说，他都不会走的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你怎么知他不会走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他若是肯走的那种人，你也不会这么样对他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道你的意思，可是……我只能要她不去杀人，却无法要她不去爱人，是么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "决斗的时候还未到，他先到这里来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "高手间的决斗，不但要看武功之强弱，还要看天时、地利、人和，上官金虹选择这里作战场，当然有他的用意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "什么用意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他想必对这里的地形很熟悉，而且说不定还会先到这里来设下埋伏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "所以李寻欢也一定要先到这里来瞧瞧，先熟悉这里地形，再看看上官金虹会在什么地方设埋伏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不错，古来的名将，在大战之前，也必定都会到战场上去巡视一遍，无论哪一种战争，若有一方先占了地利，就占了优势。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "可是他为什么一直要在这里逛来逛去呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他这么逛来逛去当然也有目的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他要先将这里每一寸土地都走一遍，看看这里的土质是坚硬，还是柔软？是干燥，还是潮湿？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那又有什么用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "因为土质的不同，可以影响轻功，你同样使出七分力，在软而潮湿的地上若是只能跃起两丈，在硬而干燥的地上就能跃起两丈五寸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那相差得也不多呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "高手相争，是连一分一寸都差不得的！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他站在这里发呆，又是为了什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 76,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    }
  ],
